title: Virtua Cop 2
description: This is an old game.It's OK if you just want to shoot up criminals---Manufacturer's Description The smash arcade hit now on your PC! Vicious Gangs are on the rampage in Virtua City! New dangers threaten the innocent! It's up to the Virtua Cops, with their new partner Janet, to wipe crime off the streets once and for all.Use compatable mode in XP and Vista if it dosn't work
